Gradle setup:

1. Download binaries from https://gradle.org/releases/
2. Unzip and install binaries: unzip -d ~/gradle/
3. Make sure the System path is corrrectly configured to the install directory: 
export PATH=/home/$USER/tools/bin/gradle-7.6.1/bin:$PATH
4. Check if gradle is installed: gradle -v
5. Configure gradle build using init plugin: 
gradle init. Select the options for configuring application/library etc.
6. Run the gradle wrapper command:
gradle wrapper
7. Check if gradle is working fine, run:
./gradle tasks

Intellij setup:
1. Import project from existing resource and pass the settings gradle file


Spring boot setup:
1. https://docs.spring.io/spring-boot/docs/current/reference/html/build-tool-plugins.html#build-tool-plugins.gradle
